::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 146.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' That IPC guy will show up in {{Color|keyword|nobold=1|fifteen days}}. I've got to become a swordmaster by then!
::{{A|VO side2 baishi yunli 118.ogg}} '''Yunli:''' Becoming a swordmaster in a mere fifteen days is quite challenging.
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 147.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' But we can't lose our momentum, Master Yunli!
::{{A|VO side2 baishi yunli 119.ogg}} '''Yunli:''' Momentum alone will only keep you going for about three days. If you really want to stick with it, you need a solid plan.
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 148 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 148 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' No worries! I've found my professional teaching assistant, (Trailblazer), to help me organize the lessons. So, there won't be any problems!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'll be sure to arrange lessons for March.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802410607-->
:::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 149 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 149 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Rest assured, masters, if not in me, at least place your faith in {{MC|f=her|m=him}}, my trusty sidekick!
:::How can you be so sure about me...?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can you be so sure about me...?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802410609-->
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 150.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Because I trust you! Even if my masters have doubts, they'll trust your judgment!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_802410610-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802410610-->
::{{A|VO side2 baishi yanqing 122.ogg}} '''Yanqing:''' Miss March is really passionate about learning swordplay, and now she has a clear goal in mind. That's a good thing for her.
::{{tx}}
::{{tx}}
::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 155 m.ogg}} {{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 155 f.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' You haven't said much, (Trailblazer). Any suggestions before we officially start training?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Mastery of the sword trumps all.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802410703-->
:::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 156.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Exactly! I prefer the cool, calm and ruthless way of doing things – that's my kind of style!
:::Friends on the road bring twists of the fate.
:::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 157.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Twists? Like the ones in those swordmaster novels? But I wonder what kind of unexpected twists I'll encounter...
:::Bump into a lonely ghost?
:::Accidentally consume a divine elixir?
:::Unlock an ingenious enigma?
:::Receive guidance from a sage?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Friends on the road bring twists of the fate.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802410705-->
:::{{A|VO side2 baishi mar7th 157.ogg}} '''March 7th:''' Twists? Like the ones in those swordmaster novels? But I wonder what kind of unexpected twists I'll encounter...
